### Çiftlik Oluştur
# Yeni çiftlik kaydı oluşturur.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Farms/Create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "ownerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "name": "Yeşil Vadi Çiftliği",
    "description": "Modern süt üretim tesisi",
    "licenseNumber": "TR-42-0001",
    "address": "Yeşilova Mah. No:15",
    "city": "Konya",
    "district": "Selçuklu",
    "neighborhood": "Yeşilova",
    "postalCode": "42100",
    "latitude": 37.8714,
    "longitude": 32.4846,
    "phoneNumber": "+905551234567",
    "email": "info@yesilvadiciftligi.com",
    "website": "www.yesilvadiciftligi.com",
    "totalArea": 500.00,
    "type": 0
}

###

### Çiftlik Güncelle
# Mevcut çiftlik bilgilerini günceller.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Farms/Update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "farmId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "name": "Yeşil Vadi Çiftliği - Güncellendi",
    "description": "Güncellenmiş açıklama",
    "licenseNumber": "TR-42-0001",
    "address": "Yeni Adres",
    "city": "Konya",
    "district": "Meram",
    "neighborhood": "Yeni Mahalle",
    "postalCode": "42200",
    "latitude": 37.8800,
    "longitude": 32.4900,
    "phoneNumber": "+905551234567",
    "email": "info@yesilvadiciftligi.com",
    "website": "www.yesilvadiciftligi.com",
    "totalArea": 600.00,
    "type": 0,
    "isVerified": true,
    "ownerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### Çiftlik Sil
# Çiftliği siler.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Farms/Delete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "farmId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "isDeleted": true
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###                              QUERIES
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Tüm Çiftlikleri Listele
# Tüm çiftlikleri listeler.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Farms/All
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
     "sorting": null,
    "filters": [],
    "pageRequest": {
        "perPageCount": 20,
        "currentPage": 1,
        "listAll": false
    }
}  

###

### Çiftlik Detayı
# Belirli bir çiftliğin detayını getirir.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Farms/Detail
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "farmId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###

### Veteriner İçin Müsait Çiftlikler
# Veteriner için atanabilecek çiftlikleri listeler.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Farms/GetAvailableForVeterinarian
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "veterinarianProfileId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
    "sorting": {
        "field": "name",
        "order": "asc"
    },
    "filters": [],
    "pageRequest": {
        "page": 1,
        "pageSize": 20
    }
}

###

### Çiftlik Seç (Pick)
# Dropdown için çiftlik listesi.
POST {{baseUrl}}/Farms/Pick
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
    "selectedIds": [],
    "keyword": "yeşil",
    "limit": 10
}
